<para><verbatim>.. module:: user_interface
:platform: Unix
:synopsis: Python module for the user Interface
.. moduleauthor:: Ammar Iqbal

Subscribes to:
/timeout to check if the timeout for the autonomous driving mode has expired

Publishes to:
/mode to start a new modality
/goalpos to send the coordinates of the goal

The User Interface is the node that lets the user switch between the modalities, including the &apos;idle&apos; one (i.e. when no mode is active). 
The command is given by a user keyboard input and it is sent to the other nodes using ROS topics.</verbatim> </para>
